  "details": "A vulnerability was determined in DTStack Taier up to 1.4.0. The affected element is the function preHandle of the file taier-data-develop/src/main/java/com/dtstack/taier/develop/interceptor/LoginInterceptor.java of the component Source Connection Test Endpoint. Executing a manipulation can lead to improper authentication. The attack may be performed from remote. The exploit has been publicly disclosed and may be utilized. This patch is called f95389e7f74acec42bcee079a616aaa06f9551d2. A patch should be applied to remediate this issue.",
